                  <summary>Two separate documents are recorded on the recto and verso of this papyrus.  The recto and verso contain accounts. The recto is a list of taxes for year 3.  The verso is perhaps a list of taxpayers. </summary>
                  <msItemStruct>
                     <note type="general">This papyrus previously had two inventory numbers (P.CtYBR inv. 70A and 70B), which have been consolidated into one.</note>
